*Galax urceolata* (Poiret) Brummitt
collected May 22, 2010 by Terry Holdsclaw
# 128

Location 35° 34.187' N; -81° 05.234' W
North slope of Anderson Mountain, 100 meters from Tower
Road on a dry, steep, wooded slope.

*Oxydendrum arboreum*, *Kalmia latifolia*, *Vaccinium vacillans*,
*Smilax herbacea* var. biltmoreana, *Smilax bona-nox* and
*Chimaphila maculata*.
